  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="Aink102-kilavi">
            ituvumatu </p>
          <p xml:lang="en">
And this is that
          </p>
        </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="Aink102">
              <l> aṉṉai vāḻivēṇ ṭaṉṉai nammūr</l>
              <l> nīṉiṟap peruṅkaṭaṟ puḷḷi ṉāṉātu</l>
                        <l> tuṉpuṟu tuyara nīṅka</l>
                        <l> viṉpuṟa vicaikkumavar tērmaṇik kuralē</l>
                        
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
              <l>Oh mother, please mother!</l>
              <l>The sound of his chariotbells will tinkle joyfully</l>
                <l>Like the [call of] birds in our town with the great, blue-hued ocean</l>
                  <l>In order for [this] endless, sorrowful grief  to go away.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
